Output demo.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 600
Set Padding 20

Type "pixel"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "pixel stats"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "pixel watch --mood happy"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "q"
Sleep 500ms

Type "pixel watch --mood hungry"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "q"
Sleep 500ms

Type "pixel watch --mood sad"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "q"
Sleep 500ms

Type "pixel watch --mood asleep"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "q"
Sleep 1s
